OL,3,CPopular wedding venue put into
OL,4,Cadministration as running costs rise
OL,6,FHestercombe House and Gardens has been
OL,7,Fput into administration after Trustees
OL,8,Fdeclared the estate is 'no longer
OL,9,Fviable in its current operational
OL,10,Fmodel'.
OL,12,FThe historic estate near Taunton
OL,13,Ffeatures a 16th century house and
OL,14,Fgardens which span four centuries of
OL,15,Fdesign which are open to the public
OL,16,Fand used as a wedding venue.
OL,18,FThe 50 acre estate includes a Georgian
OL,19,FLandscape Garden, Victorian shrubbery
OL,20,Fand Edwardian formal gardens.
