OL,3,CPopular wedding venue put into
OL,4,Cadministration as running costs rise
OL,6,FIt's staged events including a
OL,7,FChristmas Light trail, live music and
OL,8,Ftheatre and a sunflower walk.
OL,10,FForvis Mazars have been appointed
OL,11,Fadministrator of Hestercombe Gardens
OL,12,FLimited and Hestercombe Gardens Trust
OL,13,F- a charity set up in 1996 to oversee
OL,14,Frestoration of the gardens and protect
OL,15,Ftheir future.
