OL,3,CPopular wedding venue put into
OL,4,Cadministration as running costs rise
OL,6,FMark Boughey, Joint Administrator,
OL,7,Fsaid, "Visitor numbers are down over
OL,8,Fthe past year and wedding/cafe
OL,9,Foperations are failing to deliver the
OL,10,Fprofitability the wider estate
OL,11,Frequires."
OL,13,F"Despite the passion and commitment of
OL,14,Fthe current management team and
OL,15,Ffollowing a period of cost-cutting and
OL,16,Freorganisation it is sad to see a
OL,17,Fpopular and historic house and gardens
OL,18,Fleft with no real alternative but to
OL,19,Fappoint administrators to protect the
OL,20,Fasset."
