OL,6,FThe business continues to trade under
OL,7,Fthe Administrators' supervision and
OL,8,Fthe estate remains open to the public.
OL,10,FIn a statement the Trustees said
OL,11,F"Hestercombe, a beloved historic
OL,12,Festate and gardens, has played a
OL,13,Fcentral role in the cultural and
OL,14,Fsocial life of Somerset and beyond."
